abstract.text: Applies EmbeddedCare badge with custom configuration
used to integrate Felts embedded care content.
The view is meant to be presented modally or in a way that takes up the majority of your apps UI,
such as a tab in a tab bar.
Applies automatic EmbeddedCare badge to this tab using the shared badge state
Use this on individual tab content views within a TabView that has .automaticEmbeddedCareBadging()
Automatically syncs this views badge with EmbeddedCare badge state (simple API)
Automatically syncs this tab with EmbeddedCare badge state
Applies EmbeddedCare badge to this view using a shared badge state
Present a sheet with push notification permission request
Automatically applies EmbeddedCare badge integration to this TabView
This method should be called on TabView to enable automatic badge synchronization.
Automatically present push notification permission request when appropriate
